---
title: Creamy Pork Sausage & Broccoli Farfalle with Fennel & Parmesan
description: Here's a neat trick: squeeze the pork sausage meat out of the casings in small pieces to make mini meatballs! Add some broccoli and baby spinach for green goodness, toss with farfalle and you've got a pasta dish that's a sure-fire winner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5ddf04b3f28e50286f468606-9ceb5370.jpg
